The paper deals with deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also mentions the use of supervised learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper uses toy problems to demonstrate the issue, which is a common approach in the field of machine learning, specifically in deep learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper mentions the use of a second model to predict the probability of catastrophe, which is a common approach in computer vision, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV).
